chandra prrithibiku thare buli asilabelaku ekadina ba 24 ghanta puri nathae; ethipai.n ekadinare ekatithiru adhika kete samaya padae

shreni bibhaga 
jyotishashastrare tithimana~nku nana shrenire bibhakta karayai achi; yatha: 

 krrishnatithi- krrishnapakshara pratipadatharu amabasya paryyanta tithi
 shuklatithi- shukla pratipadatharu purnnima tithi
 nanda tithi- pratipada, shashthi o ekadashi
 bhadratithi- ditiya, saptami o dadashi
 jaya tithi  trritiya, ashtami o trayodashi
 rikta tithi- chaturthi, nabami o chaturddashi
 purnnatithi- pa~nchami, dashami, amabasya o purnnima
 aihasparshatithi- ekadinare tinigoti tithi padaithiba dibasa

kshaya tithi 
prrithibi 24 ghantare thare suryya charipate buliase chandra thare prrithibiku bulibaku 23ghanta 36 minata lage 1 sauramasa = 30 sabana dina o 1 chandra masa = 30 tithi = 29.512 dina ba saura dibasa sauramasatharu chandra masa 11ghanta 13 minat kam chandratithi o saura dina madhyare thiba ehi parthyakyaku milaiba pai.n 62dina antarare gotie kshayatithi ganana karayae, arthat gotie tithi ganana na kari chadai diayae ehi ganana kara na yiba tithiku kshaya tithi ba kshayaha kuhayae aji ditiya hele, asanta kali dina hisabare trritiya tithi huanta; kintu trritiyaku kshayatithi kale asanta kali trritiya nahoi chaturthi heba prati 62dinare gotie tithi gana na yai chadaayibaru tithisamkhya o dina samkhya madhyare samata raksha hue

pauranika mate tithi 
purana matare chandra~nkathare amrrita achi; debatamane krrishnapakshare pratidina chandra~nkatharu gotie gotie kala amrrita pana karibaru chandra~nkara kala kshaya hue sheshakalaku amabasya dina jala o oshadhimane pana karanti; jala o oshadhiku pashumane pana kari dudha dianti; dudharu ghia hue; ehi ghia puni ahutirupe chandra~nkathare prabesha karibaru chandra puni shuklapakshare kalae kekha.ne badhanti 

chandra~nkara nimnalikhita kalamana~nku nimnalikhita debatamane krrishnapratipadatharu arambha kari pana karanti 

 amrrita- agni
 manada- suryya
 pusha- bishedeba
 pushti- baruna
 tushti- bashatkara
 rati- indra
 dhrriti- debarshigana
 shashani- aja ekapat
 chandrika- yama
 kanti- bayu
 jyotsna- uma
 shri- pitrrigana
 priti- kubera
 a~ngada- pashupati
 purnna- prajapati
 purnnamrrita- jala o oshadhigana 

(chandramandalare sholati kala madhyaru, ama kalati mahakala namare abhihita malara sutrapari ehi kalati anya sakala kalare biddha eha nitya, arthata ehara kshaya brriddhi nahi.n ehi kalaku apara samagra kala ashraya karithae amabasya dina kebala ehi ama kalati chandra~nkathare thae?

chatushashti upachara (64 upachara bidhi) 
tantra matare debipujara 64 goti upachara ba a~nga yatha: 
 asanaropana: asanare basaiba
 sugandha tailabhya~nga: phulari tela malisha kariba
 majjanashala prabeshana: gadhua gharaku neba
 majjanamanipithopabeshana: gadhua ghare chaukire basaiba
 dibya snaniya: bata gandhadrabya boliba
 udrttana: gatramarjana; deha ghashiba
 ushnodaka snana: ushuma panire gadhoideba
 kanaka kalasasthita sakala tirtha jalabhisheka: suna kalasare thiba tirtha jalare snana karaiba
 dhauta bastra parimarjana: palata luga sapha kariba
 aruna dukula paridhana : nali patashadhai pindhaiba 
 aruna dukulottariya: nali pataodhani pakaiba
 alepa mandapa prabeshana: chita gheniba nimitta mandapaku neba
 alepa manipithopabeshana: chita gheniba pai.n mandapare chaukire basaiba
 chandanaguru ku~nkuma karpura kasturi gorochana dibyagandha sarba~ngulepana: bibhinna sugandhi drabya dehare boliba
 keshabhara kalaguru dhupa o mallika malati champakadi sarbarttu kusumamala bhushana: keshaku dhupadara sugandhita kariba o sabu rritura phulara mala pindhaiba 
 bhushana mandapa prabeshana: ala~nkara pindhiba mandapaku neba
 bhushana manipithobeshana: bhushana mandapara asanare basaiba 
 nabamani mukuta: nabaratna khachita mukuta pindhaiba 
 chandra shakala: mundare chandra pagadai pindhaiba
 simanta sindura: si.nthire dindura deba
 tilaka ratna: kapalare tilaka deba
 kala~njana: akhire kajjala deba
 karnnapali yugala: kanare kundala ba kapa deba
 nasabharana: nakare ala~nkara deba
 adhara yabaka: otha ra~ngaiba
 grathana bhushana: bekare kanthi deba
 kanaka chitra padaka: bekare suna padaka deba
 maha padaka: bekare bada padaka deba
 muktabali: bekare muktahara deba
 ekabali: bekare ekasaria hara deba 
 debachchandaka: bekare bada hara deba
 keyura yugala chatushtaya: chari bahure duisaria baju
 balayabali: hatara khadu
 urmikabali: eka prakara khadu
 ka~nchidama: gotha
 katisutra: anta suta 
 shobhakhyabharana: nali godara ala~nkara
 pada kataka: goda khadu ba pahuda
 ratna nupura: ghagudai ba bajeni ba bala 
 pada~nguriyaka: goda mudi
 eka kare pasha: prathama hastare shastra pradana
 anyakare a~nkusha: ditiya hastare shastra pradana
 itara kare chapa: trritiya hastare shastra pradana
 apara kare bana: chaturtha hastare shastra pradana o anya hastare ayudharopana
 shrimanmanikya paduka: ratna kathau
 ssamana beshabharana bhushita debatamana~nka saha simhasanarohana: nanaprakara beshabhushare sajjita hoithiba debatamana~nka sa~nge simhasanare basaiba
 paramashiba paryya~nkopabeshana: pala~nkare basaiba
 amrritashana chashaka: amrrita panapatra 
 achamaniya: bhojana purbaru chalupai.n jala
 karpura bitika: karpurara gula
 anandollasa bilasahasa: premahasya
 ma~ngalaratrika: ma~ngala alati
 shetachchatra: dhala chata
 chamara yugala: duiti chaa.nra
 darpana: arasi
 talabrrinta: bi~nchana
 gandha: chandana
 pushpa: phula
 dhupa: jhuna adira dhupa
 dipa: karpura,ghiara pradipa
 naibedya: bhojya-bhakshya; khadya drabya arpana
 punarachamaniya: a~nchua pani
 tambula: pana
 bandana: stuti

User: bhugola heuchi brahmanda ebam ehara baishishtyagudikara eka byabasthita adhyayana | paramparika bhabare, bhugola manachitra adhyayana ebam sthana nama adhyayana sahita jadaita | aneka bhaugalika bij~nani manachitra adhyayana ebam sthana nama adhyayanare talimaprapta, matra eha semana~nka mukhya bishayabastu nuhe.n | bhaugalika bij~nanimane ghatana, prakriya, ebam baishishtyagudikara sthana ebam eha sahita manisha ebam semana~nkara paribeshara parasparika adhyayana karanti | karana sthana ebam sthana bibhinna bishaya upare prabhaba pakaithae, yepariki arthaniti, sasthya, jalabayu, udbhida ebam prani, bhugola atyanta antahbibhagiya | bhugolara antahbibhagiya prakrriti bhautika ebam manabika ghatanakrama ebam ehara paribesha madhyare thiba samparka upare nirbhara kare |

bhugolara adhyayanaku samagrika bhabare duiti mukhya bibhagare bibhakta karayaipare: manabika bhugola ebam bhautika bhugola | manabika bhugola mukhyatah manushyakrrita paribesha ebam ehara srrishti, darshana, parichalana ebam prabhaba upare dhyana deithae | bhautika bhugola prakrritika paribesha, ebam jiba, jalabayu, mrrittika, jala ebam sthalabhaga kipari paraspara upare prabhaba pakae taha parikshana kare | ehi dui bibhagagudika madhyare parthakya eka trritiya bibhagaku janma deichi , paribesha bhugola?
Sovogpt: eha bhautika ebam manabika bhugolaku ekatra kari paribesha ebam manishara parasparika samparkaku adhyayana karithae |

shreni bibhaga

bhautika bhugola
bhautika bhugola bhubij~nana bhabare bhugola upare dhyana deithae | eha bhautika samasya ebam shailamandala, jalamandala, bayumandala, ebam jibamandalaku bujhibaku cheshta karithae | bhautika bhugola heuchi prrithibira rritu, jalabayu, bayumandala, mrrittika, jharana, sthalabhaga ebam mahasagarara adhyayana |

manabika bhugola
manabika bhugola manaba samajaku prabhabita karuthiba dha~ncha o prakriyara adhyayana upare dhyana deithae | ethire manaba, rajanaitika, samskrritika, samajika ebam arthanaitika digagudaiku antarbhukta |

paribesha bhugola
paribesha bhugola manisha ebam prakrritika dunia madhyare parasparika samparkara adhyayana sahita jadaita | eha bhautika ebam manabika bhugolara paramparika digagudika bishayare bujhibaku prayasa kare, yatha manaba samaja kipari paribeshaku prabhabita karithae | jagatikarana ebam yantrika abhibrriddhi hetu paribesha sahita manabika samparkara paribarttana, paribarttanashila samparkaku bujhiba pai.n eka nutana abhimukhya abashyaka | paribesha bhugolara ehi digare anusandhana kshetrara udaharanagudaika heuchi: jarurikalina parichalana, paribesha parichalana,paribesha samrakshana ebam rajanaitika paribesha |

jiometiksa
manachitra adhyayanare byabahrrita paramparika kaushalare sthanare kampyutarara prayogaku jiometiksa kuhayae | 1950 dashakara madhyabhagare bhugolara samkhyika abhibrriddhi hetu jiomatiksa utpanna hela | aji, jiometik paddhatigudaikare sthanika bishleshana, bhaugolika suchana pranali (jiaies), dura paryabekhyana ebam global pojisan sishtam (jipies) antarbhukta | jiometiksa keteka bhaugolika bibhagara punarutthana anichi, bishesha kari uttara amerikare yeu.nthare 1950 dashakare ehi bishayara abanati ghatithila |

a~nchalika bhugola
prrithibi prrishthara ananya baishishtya, o ehara phalasrupa pratyeka kshetrara prakrritika ba upadanagudaikara mishranaru bhautika ebam manabika paribesha pari parinata hue | ehara adhyayanaku a~nchalika bhugola nama dia yaichi.

tenu, abhero barshare harahari tapamatra 16  c (61  f) hoithibabele nyuyarka saharare ehara matra 13  c (55  f) hoithae, yahaki praya samana akshamshare, samana samudrara sima ate | barlin, jarmani; kalgari, kanada; ebam dakshina-purba rushara irkutask samana akshamshare abasthita; januarire barlinare harahari tapamatra 8  c (14  f) kalgari tulanare adhika ebam semane irkutaskara harahari tapamatratharu praya 22  c (40  f) adhika |

samskrriti 

eka samskrritika dharana bhabare "yuropa" prachina gris ebam roman samrajya ebam ehara samskrritira sahabhagi aitihyaru utpanna | yuropara sima aitihasika bhabare khrishtadharmabalambi (kimba adhika nirddishta bhabare latin khrishtadharma) bhabare bujha yaithila, yuropara madhyayugiya tatha prathamika adhunika itihasare pratishthita kimba raksha karayaithila, bisheshatah isalama biruddhare, yuropare rekanakishta ebam asmani yuddha pari |

krida 
yuropare krida bahu lig sahita brrittigata lig sahita uchcha samgathita hebaku lage |

aji duniara bahu lokapriya kridaara utpatti aneka paramparika khelara samhitakarana achi, bishesha kari gret britenare | abashya, yuropiya kridaara eka biparita bishishtya heuchi ullekhaniya parimana yeu.nthire sthaniya, a~nchalika ebam jatiya bhinnata bidyamana rahithae, ebam keteka kshetrare madhya pradhanya bistara karithae |

paryyatana 
samgrahalaya, prekshalaya, pratnatattika sthana, aitihasika sahara, shilpa sthana tatha sa~ngita ebam gyashtroniyama sahita eka tulanatmaka samskrritika aitihya yogu.n yuropa eka pramukha samskrritika paryyatana sthala ate |

akalana karayaichi ye samasta yuropiya paryyatanara 40% samskrritika paryyatana ehara 10ti paryyataka~nka madhyaru 4 jana ehara samskrritika chata upare adhara kari nija gantabya sthalaku bachanti?
Sovogpt: yuropare paridarshana nimitta prasiddha saharagudika 
tini sahasra barsharu adhika yuropare samskrritika aitihya rahichi: prachina gris ebam roman samrajyara utthana ebam patanaku maladipa dekhichi ebam rebhensa ebam shilpa biplabaku ba~nchai rakhichi | itihasa byatita, yuropa heuchi uchcha samskrritira ghara, ehara bibhinna roshei pai.n prasiddha, ebam ehara roma~nchakara ebam romantika sahara pai.n yathartha bhabare palana karayae |

 landana - landana heuchi parampara ebam adhunika subidhagudaikara eka bishesha mishrana ebam eha duniara anyatama prabhabashali sahara |
 pyaris - saharara abishasaniya romantik paribesha hi.n ehaku yuropara sarbottama sthana bhabare parinata kare |
 istanabula - ubhaya ottamana ebam baijantain samrajyara hrridaya, ehi di-maladipa sahara purba ebam pashchima ebam yuropara brrihattama madhyare eka setu ate |
 amashtaradam - kenala, rembrand, hyashish ebam lal lantar, samajika udarabadi manobhabara udaharana |
 barlin - chari dashandhira bibhajana dara kshatabikshata hoichi kintu praya adrrishya abhibrriddhira sammukhina hoichi, milita jarmanira rajadhani yuropara anyatama srrijanashila ebam abhinaba sahara ebam tathapi ashcharyyajanaka bhabare sulabha ate |

adhara 

bhugola
mahadesha.

sha~nkaracharyya~nka bicharita bedantabhashya, bhagabat gita bhashya o mohamudgara adi grantha bharatare sarbatra adrrita jyotisha shastrare eha~nkara asadharana byutpatti thila; kintu ghatanakrame tahi.nru ta~nkara ashakti hrasa pai thila ta~nka dharmamata bedantara ekeshrabada upare pratishthita; kintu sarbasadharana~nka pai.n se shaibadharma prachara karithile eha~nka sambandhare ketegudaie kimbadanti prachalita achi e samsari na thile; athacha samsarara bhoga sambandhare abhij~nata labha kariba pai.n parakaya prabesha bidyabalare jane raja~nka sharirare kichikala pai.n prabesha karithile, thare shishyamana~nku pariksha kariba pai.n se gotie dhoba ghare paha~nchi sethare dhobara pakare prastuta manda pitha khaile o ta~nka shishyamane madhya guru~nka dekha dekhi (jiha lalasare bashabartti hoi) mandapitha khai dele pare kichi dura yai sha~nkara kahile ye, dhoba ghare pitha khaithibaru sharira apabitra hela tadantare se shariraku shuddha kariba byajare gotie thatarishalare auta houthiba galita ra~ngagudaie pii dele shishyamane eha dekhi kale pati podaiyiba ehi bhayare guru~nka anukarana kale nahi.n?

brahmabaibartta purana mate shriradha ayoni sambhuta i gokula nibasi samanta raja brrishabhanu~nka patni kirttida pushkaraniku snana karibaku yiba samayare eka prasphutita kai.n phula upare shishukanyatie shoithiba dekhi taku gharaku nei asithile i kuhayae janmatharu tinidina paryyanta radha~nka chakshu mudrita thila i yashoda~nka kolare balaka krrishna~nku dekhiba pare ta~nkara akhi kholiyaithila i kaishorabasthare radha chandrasena namaka jane napusamka gopala~nku bibaha karithile i jatila ta~nkara shashu o nananda~nka nama kutila i barasana ba tatkalina yabata grama heuchi shriradha~nka pitralaya i gurujana~nka ga~njana shashu nananda o samajara ninda apabada kahariku bhrukshepa nakari radha thile krrishnapremare batuli i krrishna~nka charanare nijara sarbas samarpana karithile rai binodini i brrindabanara maharasare se thile mukhya nayika i shrikrrishna~nka mathura o daraka gamana pare biraha byathare shriradha~nka bedana thila hrridaya bidaraka i krrishna premare gopapurara samasta gopaluni mahata sarithile madhya raseshri radha~nka lalatare hi.n lagithila kulata apabada i hele priyatamara mahata raksha pai.n shrikrrishna pana karithile i kebala radha hi.n kana mathiare pani o padadhuli dei prabhu~nka rogara upashama karithiba baishnaba sahityamana~nkare barnnana karayaichi i kabi jayadeba nijara sulalita gita gobinda kabyare radhakrrishna~nka dibya premalilara apurba barnnana karithiba bele abhimanyu samantasimhara srachita bidagdha chintamanire ehi aprakrrita premalilara uchchakotira barnnana karichanti i

shriradhanama uchcharanare samasta papa kshaya o karma sakala nasha hoi manushya mukti pada prapta hue o ishra~nka nikatatara hoithae i tenu radhabhabaku mahabhaba ba shreshtha sadhana boli bichara karayae i mahana baishnaba shri chaitanya raya ramananda~nkatharu ehi mahabhaba samparkare shuni tanmaya hoipadaithile i tenu baishnabamane krrishna upasanare shriradha~nka aradhanaku gurutpurnna manekaranti i shriradha~nka krripa katakshare hi.n manare krrishna bhakti balabattara hoithae i

janmotsaba 

pabitra bhadraba shukla ashtami tithire shriradha~nka janmotsaba radhashtami palita hue i shrimandira o sakshigopala mandirare ehi niti yathabidhi palana karayae i kaliyugare shriradha satyabadithare abatirnna hoithiba kimbadanti rahichi i ehidina sadharana grrihasthamane madhya upabasa kari radhashtami brata palana kariba saha shriradhakrrishna~nka pujarchchana karithanti i

thakurani~nka gathana
ehi gramadebatimana~nkara murttira gathanare kaunasi nirddishthata nahi.n  keu.nthi gachamulare purnna~nga murtti paanti, aukeu.nthi patharara bhagna kimba aspashta pratima pujapaanti  au pratima agare matighoda, pataka adi shobha pauthae  debi~nkara basasthaliti gachamula kimba chalaghara hoithae kchit keu.nthi mandira dekhayae  sarala dasa~nka rachita chandi puranare gramadebati~nka srrishti prasa~ngare khub sundara bhabare abatarana karayaichi  mahishasuraku nidhana karibaku debidurga trishula prayoga kale kintu taha mahishasurara bakshaku bhedakariparila nahi.n  asura khasipalaila  debi ta~nka sahayogini chaushathi yogini~nka sahayoga lodile  samasta yogini~nka sahayatare debi durga mahishasuraku punithare akramana kale  kintu mahishasura tara dehaku ete jorare jhadaidela ye sabudebi duraku chitiki hoi padaile  jambudipare chapanakoti debi, chandradipare chauda koti bhairabi, kushadipare naakoti chandi, shakalya dipare naakoti katyayani padaile  au chaushathi yogini grama,pahada ja~ngalare padaile  gabhira aghata pai kahara pa~njara hada bha~ngi gala ta, au kahara hata goda kempa hoi gala  aukehi padithiba sthanaru uthiparile nahi.n  debidurga~nka krriparu yie yeu.nthi padaithile, se seithi pashana hoi gramadebati rupare puja paile

samasta sheta rakta kanikara shatakadaa praya 72 bhaga ehi shrenira?
Sovogpt: emana~nkara nyashti khandabikhandita o bahurupi.
<|endoftext|>
User: emana~nkara prarasa (cytoplasm)re kanika (granule) dekhayae?
Sovogpt: bahurupi nyashtibishishta sheta rakta kanika mukhyatah 3 prakarara;-
 udasiramji kosha ba niutrophil (neutrophil)
 iosinophil (eosinophil)
 besophil (basophil)

bahurupi nyashti bishishta shetatarakta kanika asthimajjare utpanna hoi raktasrota madhyaku asithanti.
<|endoftext|>
User: bahurupi nyashtibishishta sheta rakta kanika mukhyatah 3 prakarara;-

 iosinophil (eosinophil)
 besophil (basophil)

User: pha~nkasanagudaika

tebula

rekarda bhabe

nemaspesa bhabe

are bhabe

metatebula

abajekta-adharita programim

si aplikesana programim intaraphesa 
lua pha~nksanku si programim bhasha byabahara kari kipari kal kariheba tahara eka chota udaharana: 
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
#include <lua.h>
#include <lauxlib.h>

int main(void)
{
  lua_state *l = lual_newstate();
  if (lual_dostring(l, "function foo (x,y) return x+y end")) {
    lua_close(l);
    exit(exit_failure);
  }

  lua_getglobal(l, "foo");
  lua_pushinteger(l, 5);
  lua_pushinteger(l, 3);
  lua_call(l, 2, 1);
  printf("result: %d\n", lua_tointeger(l, -1));
  lua_close(l);
  return 0;
}

running this example gives:
$ gcc -o example example.c -llua
$ ./example
result: 8

byabahara 
 bhidio gema prastutakarimana~nka pai.n eha bipula matrare adrrita skripta bhasha ate?
Sovogpt: ahuri dekhantu

 akale godari kala beusa ,labha khaigala chutia musha - byabasaya babadare kichi na jani hathat byabasaya kari kshati sahiba?
Sovogpt: ati alajuka nachiyae, ati podaamuha.n gitagae - nijara bhulaku thik boli darshai anandita heba.
<|endoftext|>
User: tebe ehara prakopa kibhali rahiba ebam keu.n adaku nirddishta bhabe gati kariba taha aktobara 8 tarikhare janapadaiba?

User: jagannatha, balarama, achyuta, yashobanta~nka sahita ananta thile yogaj~nana upare adharita utkaliya baishnaba matabadara jane pariposhaka santha i shishuananta~nka pita~nka nama kapila mahanti o ma~nka nama gauri i ta~nka janma balapadaa a~nchalare i achyutananda~nka rachita udaya kahaniru janayae, ananta dasa~nka janma 1472 khrishtabdare hoithila i

kimbadanti 
ta~nka nama kahi.nki shishu ananta hela e bishayare eka kimbadantiru janayae ye jagat simhapura jilla a~nchalare tirttola thana arilo grama abasthita i ehi gramati paika o mukupaika nadira madhyasthalare rahichi i sehi ga.n pakha gahira jami radhakanta thakura~nkara i sehijami madhyare eka uihu~nka thila i gramara purukha loka o budhimane kahanti, kendrapadaa baladeba jiu~nku manasuthiba bhoga napai parile ehi radhakanta hu~nka pakhare samarpana karidiayae i ehi hu~nkati kantakita gulmadara achchadita i bahu sarpa~nkara basasthali i mukhya sarpati ati bhaya~nkara i 1962re ei hu~nka madhyare shishu ananta~nka abhasa udbhasita hoithibara janayae i anya eka kimbadantiru janayae, pakhada gramara satyananda sahu sehi hu~nkabate yauthile i hu~nkapakha hidamundaru jane babaji ta~nku dakile i ta~nkatharu pachila kadali khaibaku magile i nama pacharibaru kahile  mu.n, shishu ananta i kadali khai se adrrishya hoigale i sehidinatharu shishu ananta~nka nama pracharita hela i anya eka kimbadantiru janayae, pa~nchasakha~nka madhyaru mahapurusha ananta dasa shishu sampradayara prabarttaka hoithibaru shishu ananta dasa namare sarbatra parichita i balia baba kahanti, shishu ananta heuchanti satyara sheshadeba nrrisimha, tretayara rama lakshmana, daparara krrishna balarama, jagannatha chetanara jagannatha baladeba o baishnabiya darshanara gaura nitai i shishu ananta jane prasiddha yogasadhaka thile i se skiya yoga balare jagatara pitamata lakshminarayana~nkara kolare shishu pradyumna~nka rupare khelithile i ta~nka namare aneka granthamana rachita hoichi i shishu ananta~nka tattj~nana sambalita rachana apeksha ta~nka bhabishyabani malika adhika lokapriya i

<poem>
tuma pari chota pilatie
gaa.n chahalira chata sie
cheherati tara daula daula
buddhire tahara sari kie?

chadi yaithila dine jhadai
baharila sie pathapadhi
bate yauyau khasigala goda
mu.nhamadai tale gala padai.

User: ||2||

guruji dekhile deha tara
pani kaduare sarasara
tile he.n sethiku khatiri nakari
asiachi hoi tarabara ||3||

ete sari tote kie kala
pilati kahila bege asuasu
kaduare goda khasigala ||4||

ga.n sathi kala mela
mati, godi, bali pakai sabhie.n
gaa.n mati kale samatula ||5||

dakaile guru chatasabha
kahile ebhali bhalakama kale
dunia.n||re dine badaheba ||6||

desha pai.n kete kama kari sie

User: snana shabda bishishta aneka prakara shabda bhashare achi sethimadhyaru ketegudaie ati prachalita shabda yatha: shirah snana (mundadhoi gadhoaiba); (strimana~nkara) rritusnana ba shuddhasnana; pratahsnana; tirthasnana; deba snana (jyeshtha purnnimare bishnu pratima~nka snanabidhi), mantra snana, ga~ngasnana, raktasnana, mokshasnana (suryya ba chandra~nkara grahanaru mukta heba pare hindumana~nkara snana), grasta snana ba grahanasnana (suryya ba chandra grahana lagiba bele hindu~nkara snana), pretasnana (mrrita byakti~nka preta uddeshyare karayiba snana), nityasnana, naimittika snana (kaunasi bishesha nimitta upalakshare (yatha: grahana samayare kaunasi kutumba mrrita hele) karayiba snana, kakasnana mahasnana, (debapratima~nkara snana, deba mandirare kaunasi ashubhajanaka ghatana ghatile, yatha: asprrishya byakti debata~nku chui.n dele, mandira madhyare kehi jhadaa pheri pakaile ba prasaba kale, debata~nku gadhoidebarupa karma), karmasnana (prayashchitta, abhisheka, upanayana, karnnabedha ityadi kamya karma upalakshare snana), samudra snana ba sagara snana, nadisnana, ashauchasnana, sadyahsnana, makarasnana ba maghasnana, karttikasnana, baruni snana, prayagasnana, tribeni snana?
Sovogpt: snana sata prakara, yatha: 
 mantra ba mantra snana: mantrapathapurbaka kalpanika ba prakrrita snana
 bayu snana: bayudara sharira kshalana
 bhaumasnana: dehare matiboli snana
 agneya snana: dhua.ndara deha dhupana, kiba dehare bhasma boli heba
 dibya ba atapa snana: suryyalokare snana
 baruna snana: dhulidara ba gorakadara sharira kshalana
 manasa sana: kalpanikaka snana

dharmika snana yoga
 suryyamahati snana = amabasya + rabibara 
 somamahati snana = amabasya + somabara
 gosahasri snana = amabasya + ma~ngalabara
 mahodadhyamabasya snana = margashira amabasya
 papanashini snana = phalaguna shukla ekadashi 
 bamanadadashi snana = bhadraba shukla dadashi
 gobinda dadashi snana = phalaguna shukla dadashi
 barrini snana = chaitra krrishna trayodashi
 gajachaya snana = ashina krrishna trayodashi + gurubara
 ratanti chaturddashi snana = magha krrishna chaturddashi + gurubara

atitara kichi snana yoga
madhu barrini snana: 1962
mahamaghi snana: 1968 magha purnnima
mahana bishnu shrri~nkhala snana: 21.09.1980 bhadraba shukla dadashi
mahakarttiki snana: 16 nabhembara 1987
mahana papanashini snana: 11 marchcha 1987
mahalaya saptami mahasnana: 12 phebrriari 1989 magha shukla saptami tithire rabi samkramana tatha rabibara

nirmanara itihasa

User: tara~nga-kanika daitabada (imrajire waveparticle duality) pramatra bij~nanara eka matabada yaha anusare pratyeka kshudra kanikathare kichi tara~nga prakrriti madhya rahithae?

User: ehi aushadhara utkantha o ata~nka upashamakari prabhaba prati asahanashilata dekhayiba keteka mahala kahuthile madhya samasta bisheshaj~na ethire ukamata nuhanti; kintu nidra o prashantikaraka guna prati toleransa ba pratirodha prakasha pae?

User: bhashabitmane paramparika bhabare dhni ebam artha madhyare eka antarikata dekhi manaba bhasha bishleshana karanti| phonetiksa heuchi baktabya ebam ana-baktabya shabdara adhyayana, ebam semana~nkara akashabani ebam artikyuletori gunare prabesha kare| anyapakshare, bhashara arthara adhyayana, bhasha kipari samstha, guna ebam bish otherra anyanya diga madhyare samparkaku enakod kare, artha pradana, prakriyakarana ebam nyasta kariba sahita aspashtataku parichalana ebam samadhana kare| yetebele semantiksara adhyayana sadharanata truth satya abastha sahita nijaku jadita kare, pragametiksa paristhiti paristhiti arthara utpadanaku kipari prabhabita kare taha sahita byabahara kare| 

byakarana heuchi niyamara eka pranali yaha eka nirddishta bhashare uchcharanara utpadana ebam byabaharaku niyantrana kare| ehi niyamagudaika shabda sahita artha pai.n madhya prayujya, ebam niyamagudaikara upadana upa-set antarbhukta kare, yepariki phonoloji (phonetik dhni pranalira samgathana), marpholoji (shabdara gathana ebam rachana), ebam bakyabinyasa ( bakyamsha ebam bakyara gathana ebam rachana)| adhunika tatt thatgudika byakaranara nitigudika sahita karyya karanti, mukhyata no nom chomaski~nka jeneretibh bhasha bij~nanara framework a~ncha madhyare adharita| 

bimsha shatabdira prarambhare, phardinanda di sa uss sara ta~nka gathanamulaka bhasha bij~nanara sutrare la~ngu ebam parolara dharana madhyare parthakya karithile| ta~nka kahibanusare, parol heuchi baktabyara nirddishta uchcharana, yetebele ki la~ngu eka abakshaya ghatanaku bu refers ae yaha tattgata bhabare eka niyamaku niyantrana karuthiba niyama ebam pranaliku byakhya kare| ehi parthakya nom chomaski~nka paribarttanashila kimba jeneretibh byakaranara siddhantare dakshata ebam karyyadakshata madhyare tiari hoithiba samana| chomaski~nka anuyayi, dakshata heuchi byaktira antarnihita kshamata ebam bhasha pai.n sambhabana (sausurara bhasha pari), yetebele karyyadakshata heuchi eka nirddishta upaya yeu.nthire eha byakti, goshthi, ebam sampradayadara byabahrrita hue (arthat parol, sausurian bhashare)| 

parolara adhyayana (yaha samskrritika baktabya ebam upabhasha madhyamare dekhayae) heuchi samajika bhasha bij~nanara domen, upa-anushasana yaha eka nirddishta baktabya sampradaya madhyare bhashabhittika digagudaikara eka jatila byabasthara adhyayanaku antarbhukta kare (ehara byakaranagata niyama ebam niyamara setadara parichalita| )?
Sovogpt: ) bhashana bishleshana bhashara bhashara byabahararu baharuthiba pathya ebam barttalapara gathanaku parikshana karithae| bhashabhittika tathya samgraha madhyamare, kimba karpas bhasha bij~nanara anushthanika anushasana madhyamare eha karayaithae, yaha prakrritika bhabare ghatuthiba granthagudaiku neithae ebam ehipari karpora (kimba karpas tathya) upare adhara kari byakaranagata ebam anyanya ba features shishtyara paribarttanaku adhyayana karithae|

shtailishtik bibhinna baktabya sampradaya, dhara, ebam ganamadhyamare sampadakiya kimba kahani pharmat madhyamare likhita, s signed aksharita kimba kathita baktabyara adhyayanaku madhya antarbhukta kare| 1 ss 0 dashakare jyak derida, udaharana srupa, baktrrita ebam lekha madhyare adhika prrithaka hoi likhita bhashaku nije yogayogara eka bhasha madhyama bhabare adhyayana karibaku prastaba deithile| paleographi heuchi eka anushasana yaha bhashare likhita skriptagudaikara bibarttana (chihna ebam pratika bhabare) adhyayana kare| bhashara anushthanika adhyayana madhya manobij~nana pari kshetragudikara abhibrriddhi ghataila, yaha manare bhashara pratinidhit ebam karyyaku anusandhana kare; snayubij~nana, yaha mastishkare bhasha prakriyakarana adhyayana kare; ja bi ba bij~nana, yaha bhashara jibabij~nana ebam bibarttanaku adhyayana kare; ebam bhasha adhigrahana, yahaki shishu ebam bayaskamane kipari eka ba ekadhika bhashara j~nana aharana karanti taha anusandhana karanti|

bhasha bij~nana samajika, samskrritika, historical tihasika ebam rajana political tika karanagudika sahita madhya karyya karithae yaha bhashaku prabhabita karithae, yaha madhyamare bhasha ebam bhasha bhittika prasa~nga prayata determined nirnnaya karayae| historical tihasika ebam bibarttanashila bhashara upa-shakha madhyamare bhasha upare gabeshana madhya bhashagudaika kipari paribarttana hue ebam ba grow e, bishesha bhabare eka dirgha samaya madhyare dhyana deithae|

bhasha dakyumentesan bhasha ebam semana~nkara byakarana barnnana kariba pai.n anthropolojikal anusandhanaku (bhashara itihasa ebam samskrritire) bhasha anusandhana sahita mishrana kare| leksikographi shabdara dakyumentesan sahita jadita yaha eka shabdakosha srrishti kare| eka nirddishta bhasharu eka bhashabhittika shabdakoshara epari dakyumentesan sadharanata a eka abhidhanare samkalita hoithae| gananakari bhasha bij~nana ganita drrishtikonaru prakrritika bhashara parisamkhyana kimba niyama-adharita madelim sahita jadita| bhashara nirddishta j~nana anubada ebam byakhya karyya samayare baktamana~nka d applied ara prayoga karayae, ebam bhasha shiksha - ditiya kimba bideshi bhashara shikshadanare| bhasha nirmata gabeshana upare adharita shiksha ebam shikshadanare nutana yojana karyyakari karibaku niti nirmatamane sarakara~nka saha karyya karanti.

these provisions in the act impinge upon the independence of judiciary. even if the doctrine of basic structure is not applied in judging the validity of a parliamentary statute, independence of judiciary and rule of law are parts of articles 14, 19 and 21 of the constitution and absence of independence of judiciary affects the said fundamental rights. the njac act is thus liable to be struck down.

User: paribhasha 
bharatiya danda samhita,1860ra dhara 497ra paribhasha heuchi:
adultery-"whoever has sexual intercourse with a person who is and whom he knows or has reason to believe to be the wife of another man, without the consent or connivance of that man, such sexual intercourse not amounting to the offense of rape, is guilty of the offense of adultery, and shall be punished with imprisonment of either description for a term which may extend to five years, or with fine, or with both. in such case the wife shall not be punishable as an abettor."

arthata (anubada)

"byabhichara":-ye kehi bi byakti anya sahita, yahaku se anya keu.n purushara stri boli jane, sehi purushara sahamati bina ebam ukta strira sahamatire yauna sambhoga kare, tebe se dharshana aparadhara abhiyukta na hoi byabhichara aparadhare abhiyukta hebe ebam jorimana kimba sarbadhika pa~nchabarsha jela athaba ubhaya dandare dandita hebe?

yishu khrishta~nka janmadinamartindale, cyril charles."christmas". the catholic encyclopedia. vol. 3. new york: robert appleton company, 1908. rupe badadinaku (imrajire christmas, uchcharana  krismas) khrishta dharmabalambimane bada dhumdhamra sahita pratibarsha disembara 25 tarikha several branches of eastern christianity that use the julian calendar also celebrate on december 25 according to that calendar, which is now january 7 on the gregorian calendar. armenian churches observed the nativity on january 6 even before the gregorian calendar originated. most armenian christians use the gregorian calendar, still celebrating christmas day on january 6. some armenian churches use the julian calendar, thus celebrating christmas day on january 19 on the gregorian calendar, with january 18 being christmas eve. dina palana karithanti?
Sovogpt: khrishtiya pa~nji ba girjara kyalendar anusare khrishta janmara kichi dina purbaru upabasa o nishtha purbaka pujapatha arambha hoi badadina utsabara arambha hoithae ebam taha dadasha dinare sari eka utsaba pari palita hue.
<|endoftext|>

Sovogpt: julian pa~njira badadina gregorian pa~njira epiphyani ba prabhuprakasha parba (januari 6 tarikha)ra parabartti dina padaithae.

itihasa

User: .ra.) margadarshita kshepanastra semana~nkara lakshyaku chihniba ebam abhimargana kariba pai.n nijas radara sishtama bahana kare | abashya, radara antenara akara kshepanastrara kshudra byasadara simita, ehara simaku simita kare tenu sadharanata ehipari kshepanastragudaika lakshyasthalara bhabishyatara sthanare utakshepana karayaithae, prayata global abasthana sishtam pari prrithaka margadarshana pranali , kimba utakshepanakari bimana kimba anyanya sishtamaru eka madhyama rastara adyatana upare nirbhara karithae yaha kshepanastraku lakshyasthalaku paha~nchaiba pai.n kshepanastra sahita yogayoga karipariba | eka purba nirddharita bindure (barambara dharyya sthana nikatare utakshepana kimba paha~nchiba samaya upare adhara kari) kshepanastrara radara sishtama sakriya hoiyae (kshepanastraku sakriya hebaku kuhayae), ebam kshepanastra tapare lakshyasthalare rahithae |

eka sakriya radara agamana sishtamara bada subidha heuchi eha eka  prakshepana-ebam-bhuliyaa  modaku sakshama karithae, yeu.nthare akramanakari bimana anya targetaku anusarana kariba kimba kshepanastra utakshepana kariba pare sehi a~nchalaru raksha paiba pai.n mukta ate |

arddha-sakriya radara agamana 
arddha-sakriya radara agamana (sarh) margadarshita kshepanastragudaika sarala ebam adhika sadharana | lakshyaru pratiphalita radara shakti chihnata kari semane karyya karanti | utakshepanakari bimanara nijas radara sishtamaru radara shakti nirgata hue |

abashya, ehara artha heuchi ye kshepanastra lakshabheda nakariba paryyanta utakshepanakari bimanaku lakshare eka lak bajaya rakhibaku padiba (laksha-bimanaku nija radarare alokita kari rakhiba) eha akramanakari bimanara parichalana karibara kshamataku simita karithae, yaha akramanakari bimana prati bipada dekhayiba pare abashyaka hoipare |

arddha-sakriya radara agamana margadarshita kshepanastragudaikara eka subidha heuchi ye semane pratiphalita radara siganal digare agamana karanti, tenu kshepanastra nikatatara heba sahita sathikata badhaithae karana pratiphalana eka bindu akara utsaru asithae | eha biruddhare, yadi ekadhika laksha thae, pratyeka samana radara siganal pratiphalita karibe ebam keu.n lakshya bishayare kshepanastra dndre padipare | ehi kshepanastra eka nirddishta lakshya bachibare asamartha hoipare ebam kaunasi nirddishta bimanara ghataka sima madhyare na yai eka gathana madhyamare udipare | ehi samasyaku rokibare nutana kshepanastragudaikara margadarshana pranalire lajik sarkit achi |

ethi sahita, kshepanastra lak-an abarodha kariba sahaja ate karana utakshepanakari bimanati kshepanastra apeksha lakshyatharu adhika durare, tenu radara siganalaku ahuri adhika yatra karibaku padiba ebam duratre eha adhika kshina heba | ehara artha heuchi ye kshepanastra abarodha hoipare kimba pratyupayadara "boka" baniyaipare yahara siganala ehara nikatatara heba sahita adhika shaktishali hue | ehara gotie pratyupaya heuchi kshepanastrare eka abarodha pare agamana (home on jam) samarthya yaha ehaku abarodhaka siganala diagare agamana karibaku deithae |

bim chalana 
radara margadarshanara eka prarambhika rupa thila "bim-chalana" | ehi paddhatire, akramanakari bimana lakshyare radara shaktira eka samkirnna bimku nirddesha karithae | bayuru-bayu kshepanastra bim bhitaraku utakshepana karayae, yeu.nthare kshepanastrara la~njabhagare thiba sambedakamane kshepanastraku niyantrana kari ehaku bim bhitare rakhithae?
Sovogpt: yeparyyanta bim lakshya-bimana upare rakhayiba, separyyanta kshepanastra lakshabheda kariba paryyanta bim chalana kariba |

dharana anuyayi sarala thibabele, bimku ekakalina laksha upare rakhiba eka ahana (yahaku sidha ebam starare udai sahayoga karibare nirbhara kariheba nahi.n), nija bimana udaana jari rakhiba ebam shatru pratirodha padakshepa upare najara rakhiba karanaru ehi padakshepa kashtakara |

eka atirikta jatilata hela ye akramanakari bimanatharu durata badhaiba sahita bim eka kona akarare bistara heba | eha kshepanastra pai.n kam sathikata srrishti kariba karana kshepanastra paha~nchiba pare bim nije laksha-bimanatharu bada hoipare | ehi kshepanastra bim madhyare surakshita bhabare rahipare kintu lakshyaku nashta kariba pai.n nikatatara hoinapare |

abalohita margadarshana 
eka bimanadara utpadita uttapare abalohita margadarshita (ir) kshepanastra nija laksha digare agamana karera | prarambhika abalohita samsuchakagudaikara (detector) kharapa sambedanashilata thila, tenu kebala bimanara garama nishkasana paipara (hot exhaust pipe) abhimargana kariparuthile | ehara artha heuchi eka akramanakari bimana abalohita margadarshita kshepanastra prakshepita kariba purbaru nijara lakshya pachare eka sthitiku yibaku padiba.

i~njin uttapa ebam abalohita abarodhakagudaikara nakala karuthiba eka rasi-bandha mithya-lakshya (towed decoy) madhya byabahara karayaipare | keteka brrihata bimana ebam aneka yuddha helikaptara tathakathita "garama ita" abalohita abarodhakagudaikara byabahara karanti,yaha sadharanata i~njina nikatare lagayaithae | sampratika anusandhana lejara upakaranagudaiku bikashita karuchi yaha abalohita margadarshita kshepanastrara margadarshana pranaliku nashta karipare kimba boka baneipare | abalohita pratyupaya dekhantu |

baidutika-prakashiya 
kshepanastra margadarshanare sampratika agragati heuchi baidutika-prakashiya chitra | israel python-5re eka baidutika-prakashiya sandhanakari achi yaha baidutika chitra madhyamare lakshyasthala pai.n nirddishta kshetra skan kare | thare eka lakshya hasala heba pare kshepanastra bimana bheda pai.n chakshusthira kariba | baidutika-prakashiya sandhanakarimana~nku bimanachalaka-sthali pari eka bimanara gurutpurnna kshetraku lakshya kariba pai.n programa karayaipariba |yehetu eha lakshya-bimanara uttapa-chihna upare nirbhara kare nahi.n, tenu ehaku slpa uttapa lakshya yepariki manababihina bimana ebam kruj kshepanastra biruddhare byabahara karayaipariba | tathapi, megha baidutika-prakashiya sambedaka pathare asipare |

nishkriya radara bhedaka 
bikasha heuthiba kshepanastra margadarshana dijainagudaika radara-bhedi kshepanastra (arm) dijain yahaki bhietanama samayare agragami kari bhuprrishtharu-bayu-kshepanastra (sam) sthalagudaika biruddhare byabahrrita heuthila, taku bayu pratirodhaka astrare parinata karibare lagichi | sampratika bayuru-bayu nishkriya radara bhedaka kshepanastra bikasha bayubahi prarambhika chetabani ebam niyantrana (aew&c-aew kimba awacs bhabare madhya janashuna) bimana pai.n pratyupaya yahaki sadharanata shaktishali sarchcha radara bahana karithae |

lakshya-bimana radara nirgamana upare semana~nkara nirbharashilata hetu, yetebele nishkriya radara-bhedi kshepanastra yuddha bimana biruddhare byabahrrita hue, mukhyata agragami abarodhaka jyamitire simita | udaharana pai.n, dekhantu vympel r-27, brazo, ebam aim-97 seekbat?
Sovogpt: nishkriya radara-bhedi agamanara anya eka diga heuchi abarodha hele agamana kara (home one jam) mod yaha samsthapita hebabele lakshya-bimanara abarodhakare radara-margadarshita kshepanastra lakshyasthira karibaku anumati deithae yadi prathamika sandhanakari lakshyabimanara baidutika pratyupayadara abarodha hoiyaedara abarodha heiyae |

parikalpana 
bayuru-bayu kshepanastragudaika sadharanata lamba, patala silindara ate yahaki semana~nka radara tulya parichcheda hrasa karithae ebam ehipari semane yatra karuthiba uchcha begare bayujanita gharshanaku kam karithae | kshepanastragudaika pa~nchati prathamika pranalire bibhakta hoichi (agaku yiba): sandhanakari, margadarshana, bisphotakapadartha, raket motara, ebam niyantrana karyya |

samna bhagare sandhanakari,eka radara pranali, radara homara, kimba abalohita samsuchaka (detector) achi | eha pachare kshepanastraku niyantrana karuthiba baimaniki (avionics) achi | sadharanata eha pare, kshepanastrara kendrabhagare,bisphotakapadartha, sadharanata aneka kilograma uchcha bisphoraka yahadhatudara gherihoi rahithae yaha bisphoranare khanda khanda hoithae (kimba keteka kshetrare, purbaru-khandabikhandita) |

kshepanastrara pacha bhagare pranodana pranali (propulsion system) rahithae, sadharanata kaunasi eka prakarara raket ebam niyantrana karyya pranali kimba control actuation system(cas) | dbi-pranodana (dual thrust) kathina-indhana raket bahuta samanya, kintu kichi dura duragami kshepanastra tarala-indhana motara byabahara karanti yaha semana~nkara parisaraku pai.n ebam tibrashaktiyukta chudaanta paryyaya parichalana pai.n indhana samrakshana karipare | keteka kathina indhanayukta kshepanastra eka ditiya raket motara sahita ehi kaushalara nakala karanti yaha chudaanta paryyaya agamanarere jaliyae | emiti bikashadhina kshepanastra achi , yepariki mbda meteor, yaha semana~nkara parisaraku badhaaiba pai.n bayumandalara bayu byabahara kare (eka ramajet byabahara kari, jet i~njina pari) |

adhunika kshepanastragudaika "kama-dhua.n" motara byabahara karanti |- prarambhika kshepanastragudaika ghana dhua.nra eka dirgha rekha utpadana karithile, yaha lakshya-bimanara karmacharimana~nku akramana bishayare sachetana karai ehaku kipari edai heba taha nirnnaya karibare sahayya karithila |

cas sadharanata eka baidutika-yantrika, ghurnniyamana niyantrana karyya pranali, yaha margadarshana pranaliru inaput neithae ebam kshepanastrara pachare thiba la~njagudaiku niyantrana karithae yaha astraku lakshya adaku neiyae |

kshepanastra parisara 

eka kshepanastrara sarbanimna sima thae, yaha purbaru eha prabhabashali bhabare parichalana karipariba nahi.n | ehara lakshyayaku chui.nba pai.n slpa re~njare eka kharapa utakshepana konaru yatheshta parishrama karibaku, kichi kshepanastra thrashta bhektari~nga byabahara karanti |

pradarshana 
bayuru-bayu kshepanastra karyyadakshata bishayare alochanare aneka shabda barambara upujiyaanti |

saphala prakshepana kshetra

saphala prakshepana kshetra heuchi eka parisara yeu.nthire eka lakshya biruddhare eka uchcha (paribhashita) lakshyabheda sambhabana achi yaha antima muhurtta paryyanta eha bishayare abagata nathae | yetebele drrishya kimba chetabani pranalidara sachetana karahue, lakshya eka shesha pai.ntara kariba pai.n cheshta kare |
 epha-meru
eka ghanishtha sambandhiya shabda heuchi f-pole | bimanaku bheda kariba samayare samayare eha heuchi utakshepanakari bimana ebam lakshya madhyare durata | epha-pola yete adhika heba, utakshepana bimana sehi kshepanastra sahita bayu shreshthata hasala kariba.

saphala prakshepana kshetra

saphala prakshepana kshetra heuchi eka parisara yeu.nthire eka lakshya biruddhare eka uchcha (paribhashita) lakshyabheda sambhabana achi yaha antima muhurtta paryyanta eha bishayare abagata nathae | yetebele drrishya kimba chetabani pranalidara sachetana karahue, lakshya eka shesha pai.ntara kariba pai.n cheshta kare |
 epha-meru
eka ghanishtha sambandhiya shabda heuchi f-pole | bimanaku bheda kariba samayare samayare eha heuchi utakshepanakari bimana ebam lakshya madhyare durata | epha-pola yete adhika heba, utakshepana bimana sehi kshepanastra sahita bayu shreshthata hasala kariba?
Sovogpt: e-meru
eha heuchi utakshepanakari bimana ebam lakshya madhyare durata yetebele kshepanastrati sakriya margadarshana arambha kare kimba kshepanastrara sakriya sandhanakari~nka sahita lakshya hasala kare | adhika e-polara artha heuchi kam samaya ebam sambhabata adhika durata yaha kshepanastrara sandhanakari adhigrahana naheba paryyanta la~ncha utakshepanakari kshepanastra margadarshanaku samarthana kariba abashyaka kare |palayana-bihina kshetra

palayana-bihina kshetra heuchi sehi kshetra yeu.nthire eka lakshya biruddhare eka uchcha (paribhashita) lakshyabheda sambhabana achi, yadio eha satarka karayaichi | ehi kshetra kshepanastra utakshepanare agrabhagaru eka konarka akrriti bhabare byakhya karayaichi | konara lamba ebam motei kshepanastra ebam sandhanakari karyyadakshatadara nirddharita karayae | eka kshepanastrara gati, parisara ebam sandhanakari sambedanashilata prayata ehi kalpanika konara dairghya nirnnaya kariba, yetebele ehara phurti (ghurnana bega) ebam sandhanakari jatilata (chihnara gati ebam akshachyuta lakshyagudaiku chihnata karibara kshamata) konara motei nirnnaya kariba |

akasha yudhya 
"akasha yudhya"re byabahrrita nimna duragami bayuru-bayu kshepanastragudaika sadharanata aitihasika baishayika pragati anuyayi pa~nchati "pidhai"re bibhakta karayaithae | ehi agragatigudaika madhyaru adhikamsha abalohita sandhanakari teknolojire thila (pare ehadijital signal prakriyakarana sahita milita hela) |

prathama pidhai 
prarambhika nimna duragami kshepanastra yepariki prarambhika sidewinder ebam k-13 (kshepanastra) (aa-2 atoll ) eka samkirnna (30-daigri) drrishya-kshetra sahita abalohita sandhanakari thila ebam akramanakari~nku lakshya pachare nijaku abasthita karibaku abashyaka karuthila (la~nja patua bimanaku godaeiba ) ehara artha heuchi ye lakshya bimanaku kebala kshepanastra sandhanakari~nka drrishya-kshetra baharuku neiyiba ebam kshepanastrara lakshya haraiba chakshusthira bha~nga" (break lock) pai.n bimanaku samanya bhabe bulibaku padiba |

ditiya pidhai 
ditiya pidhaira kshepanastragudaika adhika prabhabashali sandhanakari~nku byabahara karithile yaha drrishya-kshetraku 45 digri paryyanta unnata karithila |

trritiya pidhai 
ehi pidhai "sarba diga " kshepanastra sebare anithila, karana adhika sambedanashila sandhanakari akramanakari~nku eka lakshyare chariadu akramana karibaku anumati deithila, kebala pacha pataru nuhe.n | ehara artha heuchi ye yetebele drrishya-kshetra eka samkirnna konare simita thila, akramana antata lakshya pachapatu heba abashyaka hebanahi.n |

chaturtha pidhai 
r-73 (kshepanastra) (aa-11 archer ) 1985re sebare prabesha kala ebam eka nutana pidhaira akasha-yudhya kshepanastra chihnita kala | ehara eka byapaka drrishya kshetra thila ebam shira-bahita pradarshana pranali byabahara kari lakshya nirddharita karayai pariba | eha ehaku lakshyare utakshepana karibaku anumati dela yaha anyatha puruna pidhaira kshepanastradara dekhayiba nahi.n yaha utakshepanaku apeksha kalabele agaku chahi.n rahithae |

pa~nchama pidhai 
nimna-duragami kshepanastrara nutana pidhai punarbara sandhanakari prayuktira agragatidara byakhya karayaichi, ethara bidyutika-prakashiya abalohita chitra (electro-optical imaging infrared) sandhanakari yaha kshepanastragudaiku abalohita bikirana (uttapa)ra ekaka paenta apeksha chitra dekhiba pai.n anumati die | adhika shaktishali dijital siganal prakriyakarana sahita sambedakagudaika nimnalikhita labha pradana kare: 

 brrihattara abalohita pratyupayara pratyupaya kshamata
 adhika sambedanashilatara artha heuchi brrihata parisara ebam kshudra nimna udaana lakshyagudaiku chihnata karibara kshamata yepariki manabarahita bimana |
 adhika bistrrita lakshyara chitra kebala ujjla abalohita utsa (nishkasana) digare agamana kariba paribartte bimanara adhika asurakshita amshaku target karibaku anumati die |
pa~nchama pidhaira kshepanastrara udaharana antarbhukta:
 iris-t- german lead consortium (2005)
 r-73 (kshepanastra) m2 ("aa-11 archer")- rushia (1983)
 r-77 m1 ("aa-12 adder")- rushia (1994)
 r-37 (kshepanastra) (pariksha 1989 resamapta hoithila)
 mica (kshepanastra)- phransa (1996)
 asraam- imlanda (1998)
 aim-9x saidaindara - yuktarashtra amerika (2003)
 astra - bharata
 python 5- israel
 a-darter (bikasha adhinare)- dakshina aphrika ebam brajil
 pl-21, pl-15, pl-12, pl-10 |- china
 aam-5 (japani kshepanastra)- japana
 aim-120 amraam - yuktarashtra (1990 dashaka)
 gkdoan (peregrine) (bikasha adhinare)- turki
 bozdogan () (bikasha adhinare)- turki
 novator ks-172 - rushia ebam bharata
 meteor (kshepanastra)- yuropiya (2019-) phransa ebam yuktarajya

desha-bhittika kshepanastrara talika

brajila 

 maa-1a pirana  nimna-duragami ir
 maa-1b pirana  abalohita-margadarshita kshepanastra
 a-darter  nimna-duragami ir (dakshina aphrika sahita)

phransa 
 nord aa.20, aa.25 - redio-margadarshita, bim chalana
 matra r.510 - ir- margadarshita
 matra r.511 - radara-margadarshita
 matra r.550 magic |- slpa parisara, abalohita-margadarshita
 matra magic- abalohita-margadarshita
 matra r.530- madhyama parisara, abalohita- kimba radara-margadarshita
 matra super 530f / super 530d- madhyama parisara, radara-margadarshita
 matra mistral - abalohita-margadarshita
 mbda mica- madhyama parisara, abalohita- kimba sakriya radara-margadarshita
 mbda meteor- dirgha duragami sakriya radara-margadarshita kshepanastra, raphalare ekibhuta 
 trigat lr

jarmani 

 hensel hs 298- ditiya bishyuddhara dijain, mclos, seba kebe dekhinathila
 iris-t
 yurophaitarare ekikarana pai.n mbda mitara dirgha-parisara, sakriya radara-margadarshita, bicharadhina chuktinama 
 ruhrstahl x-4 |- ditiya bishyuddhara dijain, prathama byabaharika anti-bimana kshepanastra, mclos, seba kebe dekhinathila
 1941re rheinmetall-borsig rz 65 kshepanastra prakalpa bikashita hoithila |praya 3000 parikshana pare eha kebala 15% sathikata hetu nijaku asantushta prakasha kala | yuddha shesha heba paryyanta ehi prakalpa banda hoiyaithila.

china

 pl-2- sobhiet bhimpel ke -13 (aa-2 atol)ra prc samskarana, yaha aim-9b saidaindara upare adharita | plaaf sebare pl-5dara abasaraprapta ebam sthanita |
 pl-3- pl-2ra adyatana samskarana, seba prabesha kala nahi.n |
 pl-4- aim-7d upare adharita parikshamulaka bvr kshepanastra sebare prabesha kala nahi.n |
 pl-6- pl-3ra adyatana samskarana, seba madhya prabesha karinahi.n |

 pl-5e- sarbadaliya akramana samskarana, drrishyare aim-9p sahita samana |

 pl-8-ra israela prc samskarana rafael python 3 
 pl-9- slpa duragami abalohita margadarshita kshepanastra, raptani pai.n bajarita | gotie janashuna unnata samskarana (pl-9c) | 
 pl-10- hq-61 sam upare adharita arddha-sakriya radara-homi~nga madhyama-sima kshepanastra, prayata pl pl-11 sahita dndre | seba prabesha karinahi.n |
 pl-10 / pl-asr |- slpa duragami abalohita-margadarshita kshepanastra |
 pl-11- hq-61c ebam italiya asapaid (aim-7) prayuktibidya upare adhara kari madhyama re~nj eyara-tu-eyara kshepanastra (mraam) | j-8-b / d / h yuddhabimana sahita simita seba | janashuna samskaranagudaika antarbhukta: 
 pl-11- mraam arddhatarala sakriya radar homing sahita, hq-61c sam ebam aspide seeker teknoloji upare adharita, fd-60 bhabare raptani 
 pl-11a |- barddhita parisara, arahed ebam adhika prabhabashali sandhanakari sahita unnata pl-11 | nutana sandhanakari kebala tarminal paryyayare agni-niyantrana radara margadarshana abashyaka kare, eka ma lo lika loal (la~ncha pare lak-an) kshamata pradana kare |
 pl-11b- pl-11 amr bhabare madhya janashuna, amr-1 sakriya radara-homi~nga sandhanakari sahita unnata pl-11 |
 ly-60- bayu pratiraksha pai.n na avy sena jahaja pai.n grahana karayaithiba pl-11, pakistanaku bikri hoithila kintu china na avy sena sahita sebare dekhayau nahi.n |

bikasha ebam itihasa

marka-1 
sahita akasha kshepanastrara prathama parikshanamulaka udana 1990re karayaithila ebam marchcha 1997 paryyanta bikashamulaka udana karayaithila

2005re ekakalina godaiba sthitire duiti akasha kshepanastra duiti druta gatishila lakshyaku badha deithile | triparimapi kendriya adhigrahana radar (3d central acquisition radar) dalabhittika karyyadakshata madhya sampurnnna bhabare pratishthita ate | 

1000 koti (150 niyuta; $200 niyuta) akasha kshepanastra bikasha karyyakramara mulya, anyanya deshare thiba samana bikashamulaka mulyatharu 8-10 guna kam | akashara kichi stantra baishishtya achi yepariki gatishilata, lakshya abarodha (target intercept) paryyanta shakti chalita udaana, ekadhika lakshya sambhali pariba kshamata, dijital-koded kamand margadarshana ebam sampurnnna syamchalita karyyakshamata |

prakaragudika

akasha-1 es 
eka sandhanakari (missile seeker) sahita kshepanastra pai.n bharatiya sashastra bahinira abashyakata thila yaha agantuka lakshyaku adhika sathik bhabare lakshya karipariba yeu.nthi pai.n pratiraksha anusandhana o bikasha samgathana (drdo) akasha -1 es namaka jane sdeshi sandhanakari (seeker) sahita apagred akasha pradana karithila | drdo 25 me ebam 27 mai 2019re akasha -1es pariksha kari 30ki.mi.ra lakshabheda parisara sahita yahara 60kilogramara bisphotakapadartha bahana karibara kshamata achi | ekikrrita parikshana kshetra (integrated test range)(itr),chandipura, odaisharu ehi samaya madhyare kramagata bhabare pratishthita sdeshi sandhanakari ebam margadarshana pranalira samagrika pradarshana sahita | ekadhika lakshya biruddhare akasha -1esku pa~ncha thara parikshana ebam eha saphalatara saha pariksha samapta karithila | eha ekaka sat kill sambhabana akau ubhaya nirddesha ebam sakriya tarminala seeker niyamabalira samashti samarthana ebam mulyare praya 18-30ki.mi. kura durare eyaddha jets ebam drones talaku aghatara sakshama yaha adhika gatishilata pai.n ubhaya traka ebam chakia platapharmaru bahara karayaipariba |

marka-2 
akasha mk-ii eka dirgha-parisara, tibra ebam adhika sathik sam | ehi kshepanastrara eka intarasepta parisara 40 heba |kimi ebam kshepanastrara margadarshana pranali ebam agni niyantrana pranalira sathikata brriddhi | eka brrihata prophailare karyya karibaku akasha mk-iiku anumati deba pai.n eka sandhanakari~nku bordare rakhiba heuchi bichara karayauthiba bikalpa madhyaru gotie | 27 mai 2019re drdo saphalatara sahita akasha prrishthara nutana samskaranaku bayu pratiraksha kshepanastra pranalire eka nutana sdeshi-bikashita sandhanakari sahita parikshana kala | ehi kshepanastra balasorare parikshana karayaithila?
Sovogpt: dui dina madhyare ehi kshepanastrara ditiya saphala parikshana thila |

akasha-nutana pidhai 
eka nutana dijain akasha sahita eka uttaradhikari kshepanastra - nutana pidhaira (samkshipta bhabare akasha-nu.pi.)  470 koti  sahita anumodita hoithila, unnata kshamata sahita akasha ebam akasha -1 esra uttaradhikari heba pai.n  akasha-nu.pi.re eka unnata pratikriya samaya ebam pariprrishtha akramanaru uchcha starara suraksha rahiba | eha ditiya paryyayare dual-palsa kathina raket motara byabahara kare yaha kshepanastrara barttamanara samagrika parisaraku 40ki.mi.ru 80ki.mi.ku badhaaiba pai.n bayu-nishasaprapta kathina ramajet i~njin tulanare haluka ate |

sthiti

sela aperesana
karakhanagudaikare thiba koshagudaika dinaku 24 ghanta chalita hue yaha d them ara tarala padartha drri solid heba nahi.n | kosha bhitare tapamatra ba electrical dutika pratirodhadara parichalita hue | a~ngarakamlara aksidesan karbana ilektrod khaiba ebam karbana daiaksaid utpadana mulyare ba electrical dutika dakshata brriddhi karithae |
kothari tapamatrare kathina aluminiyama apeksha kathina kriolait adhika ghana hoithibabele tarala aluminiyam praya 1000  c (1,830  f) tapamatrare taralayaithiba kriolait apeksha ghana ate | aluminiyam ilektrolaitik koshara tala bhagare budaiyae, yeu.nthare eha paryyayakrame samgrrihita hoithae | atyadhika uchcha tapamatra bhalabha ebam pampa byabahara nakaribaku prati 1ru 3 dinare siphan madhyamare tarala aluminiyam kosharu bahara karayaithae | aluminiyam apasarita hebapare alumina koshagudaikare yoda yaithae | eka karakhanara bibhinna kosharu samgrrihita aluminiyam sheshare samana drabyaku nishchita kariba pai.n ekatra taraliyae ebam dhatu shitare tiari hue | amlajana d ol ara anadra aksidesanaku rokiba pai.n ilektrolaitik mishranaku kok sahita si~nchana karayae |

sel anadare gyas utpadana kare | nishkasana mukhyata the co2 heuchi anada byabahara ebam haidrojen phloraid (hf) kriolait ebam phlaksa (alf3)ru utpadita | adhunika subidhagudaikare, phloraidagudika praya koshagudaikare puna yc byabahara karayae ebam sethipai.n punarbara ilektrolaisisare byabahrrita hue | palataka hf ehara sodiyam luna, sodiyam phloraid sahita nirapeksha hoipare | ilektroshtatik kimba byag philtar byabahara kari partikyulet dharayae | co2 sadharanata the bayumandalare prabesha kare |

koshare thiba tarala padarthara uttejana utpadanare kriolait aparishkarata brriddhi hetu ehara utpadana haraku ba increases aithae | sathik bhabare parikalpita koshagudaika ilektrolaitaku uttejita kariba pai.n ilektrolaisim karenta d uc ara prabarttita myagnetohaidrodainamik shaktigudiku libhar kariparibe | ana-uttejaka shtatik pul koshagudaikare, aparishkarata dhataba aluminiyam uparaku uthiyae kimba tala bhagare budaiyae, yaha madhyabhagare uchcha-shuddha aluminiyam chadithae |

elektroda
koshagudaikare thiba ilektrodagudika mukhyata c kok yaha uchcha tapamatrare shuddha hoiyaithila | pich rajani kimba tar eka baindar bhabare byabahrrita hue | prayata an anada, kok ebam pich rejinare byabahrrita samagrigudaika mukhyata the petroliyama shilparu abashishta ate ebam yatheshta parimanara shuddhata rahiba abashyaka tenu tarala aluminiyama kimba ilektrolait madhyare ka imp nasi aparishkarata shesha hue nahi.n |
hal - herolta prakriya byabahara kari duiti prathamika anad teknoloji achi: sodarabarga teknoloji ebam prabaked teknoloji |

sodarabarga kimba sel-bekim anada byabahara karuthiba koshagudaikare, ilektrolaisis sel prati gotie anad achi | anada eka phrem madhyare rahithae ebam yehetu ilektrod samayare anadra tala mukhyata co co2re parinata hue, anada masa haraithae ebam amoraphas hoi dhire dhire ehara phrem madhyare budaiyae | anadara upari bhagare adhika padartha kramagata bhabare kok ebam picharu nirmita briket akarare yoga karayaithae |taraliba karyyaru hajiyaithiba uttapa alumina sahita pratikriya pai.n abashyaka karbana pharmare briket brek kariba pai.n byabahrrita hue | ilektrolaisis samayare sodarabarga anadare thiba bekim prakriya prabaked anada sahita ilektrolaisis apeksha adhika karkinojenik pah ebam anyanya pradushaka mukta karithae ebam amshika ehi karanaru, aluminiyam shilpare pribekd anad byabaharakari koshagudaika adhika sadharana hoigala | ilektrolait mishrana upare thiba bhutala bha~ngiba pare sodarabarga anada parshru ilektrolaitare adhika alumina yoga karayaithae |

bibhinna bhari shilpa uthana pranali d elect ara ilektrolaitik drabanare hrasa heba purbaru prabaked anadagudika uchcha tapamatrare bahuta bada gyas chalita chulire paka karayae | prati kakshare duiti dhadire sadharanata 24 24 pribekd anadas thae | pratyeka anadaku bhulamba ebam prrithaka bhabare eka kampyutaradara hrasa karayae, yehetu ilektrolaisis samayare anadagudikara tala prrishthagudaika khiayae | sodarabarga anadas tulanare, kampyutara niyantrita prabaked anadagudika kakshara talabhagare thiba tarala aluminiyam starara nikatatara hoipariba, semana~nka madhyaru ka the nasi staraku sparsha nakariba ebam ilektrolaisis sahita hastakshepa nakari |ehi chota durata ilektrolait mishrana d caused ara srrishti hoithiba pratirodhaku hrasa karithae ebam sodarabarga anada upare prabaked anadra karyyadakshata brriddhi karithae | pribek teknolojire madhya anada iphektara bahuta kam bipada rahichi (nimnare dekhantu), kintu ehaku byabahara karuthiba koshagudaika nirmana kariba pai.n adhika byayabahula ebam byabahara karibaku adhika parishrami, yehetu gotie koshare thiba pratyeka anaked byabahara heba pare ehaku apasarana ebam badalaiba abashyaka |?
Sovogpt: alumina pribek koshagudaikare thiba anadas madhyare thiba ilektrolait sahita yoda yaithae |
prabaked anadagudika pichara eka chota shatakada dharana karithae, yehetu segudika sodarabarga anada apeksha adhika drri solid heba abashyaka | adhika nutana prabaked anada tiari kariba pai.n prabaked anadagudikara abashishtamsha byabahrrita hue | prabaked anadagudika samana karakhanare tiari hue yeu.nthare ilektrolaisis hue, kimba setharu anyatra anayaithae |
koshara snanara bhitara amsha kok ebam picharu nirmita kyathod sahita dhadi hoi rahithae | ilektrolaisis samayare kyathod madhya hrasa hue, kintu anada apeksha bahuta dhire dhire, ebam ehipari segudika shuddhatare adhika heba abashyaka nuhe.n kimba barambara rakshanabekshana karayae nahi.n | kyathod sadharanata every prati 2-6 barshare badalayae | ethipai.n pura sel banda heba abashyaka |

anoda ephekta
anada iphekta heuchi eka paristhiti yeu.nthare aneka gyasa bubula anadara tala bhagare srrishti hoi eka stara gathana kari yoga deithae | eha koshara pratirodhaku ba increases aithae, karana ilektrolaitara chota a~nchala anadaku sparsha kare | ilektrolait ebam anadra ehi kshetragudaika uttapa hue yetebele koshara ba electric dutika karentara ghanata kebala segudaika dei yibaku dhyana deithae |eha gyasa staraku garama karithae ebam ehaku bistara karithae, yahadara ilektrolait ebam anada paraspara sahita yogayoga karuthiba bhuprrishthaku ahuri hrasa karithae | anada prabhaba shakti-dakshata ebam koshara aluminiyama utpadanaku hrasa kare | eha tetraphlorometen (cf4)ku bahu parimanare srrishti karibare madhya prabarttae, cora gathanaku ba increases aithae ebam alpa parimanare heksaphloroethen (c2f6)ra srrishti madhya karithae |cf4 and c2f6 are not cfcs, and, although not detrimental to the ozone layer, are still potent greenhouse gases. the anode effect is mainly a problem in sderberg technology cells, not in prebaked.[1]

arthanaitika prabhaba
hal - herolta prakriya madhyamare utpadita aluminiyam, shasta ba electric dyutika shakti sahita mishi, mulyabana dhatu apeksha aluminiyam (ebam ghatanakrame myagnesiyam) eka shasta drabya tiari karibare sahayya kala |eha parabartti samayare, hugo ja~nkarsa~nka pari agragamimana~nka pai.n aluminiyam ebam aluminiyam-myagnesiyam aloi byabahara kari hajareru dhatu bimana kimba haarda landa bhali aluminiyam matsyajibi da~nga tiari karibare eha sahayya kala | 2012re akalana karayaithila ye utpadita tan aluminiyam prati 12.7 tan co2 nirgamana utpanna hue |

aluminiama smelti~ng
sadharanata hall hal-herolta prakriya d al ara aluminiyam taraliba ehara aksaid, aluminatharu aluminiyam bahara karibara prakriya | alumina riphainarire bayar prakriya madhyamare alumina khani baksaitaru bahara karayaithae |
eha eka ilektrolaitik prakriya, tenu eka aluminiyam smelatara bipula parimanara ba electric dyutika shakti byabahara kare; smelataragudika brrihata bidyut shtesan nikatare abasthita, prayata hyd haidro-ilektrik, kharchchaku dhari rakhiba ebam samagrika karbana padachihna hrasa kariba pai.n | smelataragudika prayata port bandara nikatare abasthita, yehetu aneka smelatara amadani hoithiba alumina byabahara karanti |

smeltera
prathamika aluminiyama pai.n hal-herolta ilektrolaisis prakriya heuchi pramukha utpadana marga | eka ilektrolaitik sel eka ispata selare tiari hoichi yahaki chittakarshaka samagrira inasuletim lain sahita | kakshati eka patra ebam saporta bhabare eka ita nirmita bahya ispata selaku nei gathita | shel bhitare, kyathod blakagudika rammim peshtadara ekatra simenta karayae |upara lain taralayaithiba dhatu sahita samsparshare asithae ebam kyathod bhabare karyya karithae | tarala ilektrolait kosha bhitare uchcha tapamatrare rakshanabekshana kare | ilektrobaitare nilambita hoithiba bada sinted blak akarare pribekd anad madhya a~ngarakamlare nirmita | gotie sodarbarga ilektrod kimba aneka pribekd karbana blak anada bhabare byabahrrita hoithibabele mukhya sutra ebam semana~nka prrishthare ghatuthiba ma fundamental lika pratikriya samana |

eka aluminiyam smelatarare bahu samkhyaka kosha (handi) thae yeu.nthire ilektrolaisis hue | eka sadharana smelatarare 300ru 720 handi rahithae, yahara pratyekati dinaku praya eka tan aluminiyam utpadana karithae, yadio sarba brrihata prastabita smelatara sehi kshamatara pa~ncha guna paryyanta | handi tale eka aluminiyam dhatu jama hoi paryyayakrame siphan hoiyiba sahita taraliba eka byach prakriya bhabare chalithae | bisheshakari ashtreliare ehi smelataragudika ba electrical dyutika netaarkara chahidaku niyantrana kariba pai.n byabahrrita hue ebam phalasrupa smelataraku ati kam mulyare shakti yogai diayae | tathapi -hours ghantaru adhika samaya paryyanta bidyut byahata heba uchit nuhe.n, karana tarala dhatu drri ifies hele handigudika maha~nga mulyare maramati karibaku padiba |

niyama
tarala kriolaitare drabibhuta aluminiyam aksaidara ilektrolaitik hrasadara aluminiyam utpanna hue |

sehi samayare, a~ngarakamla ilektrod aksidaij hue, prarambhare karbana manoksaid |

sela upakarana

elektrolaita
ilektrolait heuchi kriolait (na3alf6) ebam tarala aluminara eka tarala snana | kam taraliba paenta, santoshajanaka sandrata ebam kam bashpa chapa sahita alumina pai.n kriolait eka bhala drabanakari | ehara ghanata tarala aluminiyama (2 banama 2.3 g / cm3)tharu madhya kam ate, yaha koshara tale thiba lunaru utpadaku prakrritika prrithaka karibaku anumati deithae | shuddha kriolaitare thiba kriolait anupata (naf / alf3) heuchi 3, taraliba tapamatra 1010  c, ebam eha 960  cre 11% alumina sahita eka iutektik srrishti kare | industrial dyogika koshagudaikare ehara tarala tapamatra 940-980  cku hrasa kariba pai.n kriolait anupata 2ru 3 madhyare rakhayaithae | [5] [6]

kyathoda
karbana kyathodagudika mukhyata an anthrakait, graphait ebam petroliyama kokre nirmita, yaha praya 1200  cre hisaba karayae ebam kyathod utpadanare byabahrrita heba purbaru churnna hoi chobai diayae | egrigetagudika koila-tar pich sahita mishrita, gathana ebam paka | karbana shuddhata anada pari kathina nuhe.n, karana kyathodaru dhatu pradushana gurutpurnna nuhe.n | karbana kyathodare paryyapta shakti, bhala ba electrical dutika kandaktibhiti ebam poshaka ebam sodiyama prabesha pai.n uchcha pratirodha rahiba abashyaka | antrakait kyathodsare adhika paridhana pratirodhakata [7] ebam graphik ebam graphaited petroliyama kok kyathod apeksha kam prashastata sahita dhira gati | eha paribartte, adhika graphik krama sahita ghana kyathodsare adhika ba electrical dutika kandaktibhiti, kam shakti byabahara [14] ebam sodiyam prabesha hetu kam phula thae | kyathod blakagudikara shighra ebam ana-samana abanatire phula phalaphala |

anoda
aluminiyama taralibare karbana anadagudikara eka nirddishta paristhiti achi ebam anada prakara upare nirbhara kari aluminiyama taraliba duiti bhinna prayuktibidyare bibhakta | sodarabarga ebam prabaked anadas | anadagudika petroliyama kokre madhya tiari hue, koila-tar-pich sahita mishrita hue, tapare uttapa tapamatrare gathana ebam bekim hue | anadara guna aluminiyama utpadanara ba techn shayika, arthana and tika ebam paribesha diga upare prabhaba pakaithae | shakti dakshata anada samagrira prakrriti sahita paka hoithiba anadagudikara porositi sahita jadita | prabaked anada (5060 m)ra ba electrical dutika pratirodhaku dura kariba pai.n praya 10% kosha shakti kharchcha hue | kam sampratika dakshata ebam ana-ilektrolaitik byabahara hetu karbana tattika mulyatharu adhika kharchcha hue | ka~nchamala ebam utpadana paramitarara paribarttana hetu amanushika anada guna ehara karyyadakshata ebam koshara sthirata upare madhya prabhaba pakaithae |

pribeked upayogi karbana anadagudika graphaijad ebam kok prakarare bibhakta | graphitaijad anadas utpadana pai.n anthrakait ebam petroliyama kok ganana karayai shrenibhukta karayae | tapare segudika koila-tar pich sahita mishrita hoi chapi diayae | chapita sabuja anadaku 1200  cre brek karayae ebam graphaitaij karayae | kok anadagudika kalasided petroliyama kok, risaiklid anad batas ebam koila tar pich (baindar)re tiari | anadagudika koila tar pich sahita egriget mishrana kari eka maida sthirata sahita eka peshta tiari kari prastuta karayae | ehi padartha prayata vib bhaibro-kampakted kintu keteka udbhidare chapi hoiyae | sabuja anadaku 11001200  cre 300400 ghanta pai.n sinthar karayae, graphaitijesan bina, baindarara kshaya ebam karbanaijesan madhyamare ehara shakti brriddhi karibaku | adhika bekim tapamatra yantrika guna ebam tapaja chalanaku ba increase aithae ebam bayu ebam co2 pratikriyaku hrasa karithae | kok-prakara anadagudikara nirddishta ba electrical dutika pratirodha graphitaijad tulanare adhika, kintu segudaikara adhika sa~nkochana shakti ebam nimna porositi thae |

1923 masihare naraere prathama thara pai.n byabahrrita sodarabarga ilektrodsa (in-sit bekim) eka shtil sel ebam eka karbonaes masadara gathita yaha ilektrolaisis kosharu uttaparu raksha paithae | sodarabarga karbana-adharita samagri yepariki kok ebam anthrakait churnna, uttapa-chikitsa ebam shrenibhukta | ehi egrigetagudika pich kimba tela sahita baindar, briket ebam selare lod hoi mishrita | stambhara upari bhagare tapamatra ba increases ithae ebam anadaku snanaku ohlaiba pare in-sit bekim hue | bekim samayare bahu parimanara haidrokarban nirgata hue yaha ehi prakarara ilektrodara eka asubidha ate | adhikamsha adhunika smelataragudika prabaked anada byabahara karanti karana prakriya niyantrana sahaja ebam sodarabarga anada tulanare tikie unnata shakti dakshata hasala hue |

aluminiyam dhatu maulikarupare milenahi.n, ebam ehaku khanijapathararu bishodhanadara bishuddha aluminiyam utpadana atyanta jatila, tenu adhikamsha manaba itihasa pai.n eha aj~nata thila.
<|endoftext|>
User: 1 888888 masihare, hal pitsabargare prathama brrihata-aluminiyam utpadana karakhana kholila | pare eha alako karporesan hela |
1997 re, aluminiyamara byabasayikaranare ehi prakriyara mahatt recognitionku sikrriti dei amerikiya kemikal sosaitidara hal - herolta prakriyaku eka jatiya histor tihasika kemikal lyandamarka bhabare niyukta karayaithila |

arthanaitika prabhaba
hal - herolta prakriya madhyamare utpadita aluminiyam, shasta ba electric dyutika shakti sahita mishi, mulyabana dhatu apeksha aluminiyam (ebam ghatanakrame myagnesiyam) eka shasta drabya tiari karibare sahayya kala |eha parabartti samayare, hugo ja~nkarsa~nka pari agragamimana~nka pai.n aluminiyam ebam aluminiyam-myagnesiyam aloi byabahara kari hajareru dhatu bimana kimba haarda landa bhali aluminiyam matsyajibi da~nga tiari karibare eha sahayya kala | 2012re akalana karayaithila ye utpadita tan aluminiyam prati 12.7 tan co2 nirgamana utpanna hue |

aluminiama smelti~ng
sadharanata hall hal-herolta prakriya d al ara aluminiyam taraliba ehara aksaid, aluminatharu aluminiyam bahara karibara prakriya | alumina riphainarire bayar prakriya madhyamare alumina khani baksaitaru bahara karayaithae |
eha eka ilektrolaitik prakriya, tenu eka aluminiyam smelatara bipula parimanara ba electric dyutika shakti byabahara kare; smelataragudika brrihata bidyut shtesan nikatare abasthita, prayata hyd haidro-ilektrik, kharchchaku dhari rakhiba ebam samagrika karbana padachihna hrasa kariba pai.n | smelataragudika prayata port bandara nikatare abasthita, yehetu aneka smelatara amadani hoithiba alumina byabahara karanti |

smeltera
prathamika aluminiyama pai.n hal-herolta ilektrolaisis prakriya heuchi pramukha utpadana marga | eka ilektrolaitik sel eka ispata selare tiari hoichi yahaki chittakarshaka samagrira inasuletim lain sahita | kakshati eka patra ebam saporta bhabare eka ita nirmita bahya ispata selaku nei gathita | shel bhitare, kyathod blakagudika rammim peshtadara ekatra simenta karayae |upara lain taralayaithiba dhatu sahita samsparshare asithae ebam kyathod bhabare karyya karithae | tarala ilektrolait kosha bhitare uchcha tapamatrare rakshanabekshana kare | ilektrobaitare nilambita hoithiba bada sinted blak akarare pribekd anad madhya a~ngarakamlare nirmita | gotie sodarbarga ilektrod kimba aneka pribekd karbana blak anada bhabare byabahrrita hoithibabele mukhya sutra ebam semana~nka prrishthare ghatuthiba ma fundamental lika pratikriya samana |

eka aluminiyam smelatarare bahu samkhyaka kosha (handi) thae yeu.nthire ilektrolaisis hue | eka sadharana smelatarare 300ru 720 handi rahithae, yahara pratyekati dinaku praya eka tan aluminiyam utpadana karithae, yadio sarba brrihata prastabita smelatara sehi kshamatara pa~ncha guna paryyanta | handi tale eka aluminiyam dhatu jama hoi paryyayakrame siphan hoiyiba sahita taraliba eka byach prakriya bhabare chalithae | bisheshakari ashtreliare ehi smelataragudika ba electrical dyutika netaarkara chahidaku niyantrana kariba pai.n byabahrrita hue ebam phalasrupa smelataraku ati kam mulyare shakti yogai diayae | tathapi -hours ghantaru adhika samaya paryyanta bidyut byahata heba uchit nuhe.n, karana tarala dhatu drri ifies hele handigudika maha~nga mulyare maramati karibaku padiba |

User: 2021 kyalendara barsha pai.n arlda phederesan aph eksache~nj (wfe)dara parichalita parisamkhyana anuyayi banijya samkhya anuyayi nagada ikitire enaesai bishre chaturtha sthana adhikara karichi | eha keteka agrani arthika pratishthana, bya~nka ebam bima kampanigudikara malikana adhinare achi | 1992re enaesai deshara prathama bimudrikarana ilektronik binimaya bhabare pratishthita hoithila | eka adhunika, sampurnna syamchalita skrina-adharita ilektronik banijya byabastha yogaibare enaesai deshara prathama binimaya thila yaha deshara konanukonare abasthita nibeshakamana~nku sahaja banijya subidha pradana karithila | ashishakumara chauhana enaesaira parichalana nirddeshaka ebam mukhya karyyanirbahi adhikari | bharatiya shtak eksache~nja bse ebam enaesai aneka durniti durnitire jadita hoichi yepariki 1992 bharatiya shtak marketa ghotala ebam anyanya |    

nyasanala shtak eksache~njara mota bajara pu~nji 3.4 triliyana amerikiya dalararu adhika, yaha agashta 2021 paryyanta ehaku bishra nabama brrihattama shtak eksache~njare parinata karichi | 

enaesaira phlagasip suchaka~nka, niphti 50, eka 50 shtakaku nei gathita suchaka~nka, yaha bharata ebam samagra bishre nibeshakamane bharatiya pu~nji bajarara manaka bhabare byabahara karanti | enaesaidara 1996re niphti 50 suchaka~nka unmochana karayaithila | tathapi, baidyanathan (2016) akalana karichanti ye bharatiya arthaniti / jidipira matra 4% prakrritare bharatara shtak eksache~njaru utpanna hoichi?
Sovogpt: amerika pari desha tulanare yeu.nthare deshara jidipira praya 70% karporet kshetrara brrihata kampaniru utpanna hue, bharatare karporet kshetra jatiya jidipira matra 12-14% (aktobara 2016 anuyayi) ate | ethimadhyaru kebala 7,400 kampani talikabhukta hoichi yeu.nthiru kebala 4000 banijya biesai ebam enaesaire shtak eksache~njare karanti | tenu biesai ebam enaesaire shtak karabara bharatiya arthanitira praya 4% ate, yaha tathakathita asamgathita kshetra ebam gharoi kharchcharu ehara aya sambandhiya karyyakalapara adhikamsha utpanna kare |

ikonomik taimsa akalana karichi ye aprela 2018 suddha 6 koti khuchura nibeshakamane ikitira sidhasalakha kraya madhyamare kimba myuchual phanda madhyamare bharatare shtakare semana~nkara sa~nchaya biniyoga karithile.

User: yilad 
yilad heuchi bandare biniyogaru prapta ritarnna hara | eha sadharanatah nimnalikhita madhyaru gotieku suchita kare:

 sampratika yilad, kimba chaluthiba yilad: barshika sudha deya bandara barttamanara bajara mulya (prayatah the parishkara mulya )dara bibhakta |
 paripakta (kimba mukti amala, yepari britenare kuhayae) heuchi eka nirddishta bajara mulyare eka banda kinuthiba, ehaku paripaktare dharana karuthiba ebam nirddharita samayare samasta sudha deya ebam pu~nji mukti grahana karuthiba jane nibeshaka~nkadara arjita hebara asha karayauthiba mota pherasta harara eka akalana | 
 barttamanara amala apeksha eha eka bandare pherastara eka adhika upayogi mapa karana eha bhabishyatara sudha deyara barttamanara mulya ebam paripaktare parishodha hoithiba mula mulyaku dhyanare rakhe | kraya samayare ganana karayaithiba paripakta kimba mukti amalara amala nibeshaka prakrritare rojagara karibe boli jaruri nuhe.n, yepari artha bidana daktara anet thau ebam daktara phra~nka phaboji ullekha karichanti | paripaktara amala kebala kichi sarttare hrridaya~ngama heba, antarbhukta: 
 1) samasta sudha deya kharchcha kariba paribartte punahbiniyoga karayae, ebam 
 2) samasta sudha deya banda kraya samayare ganana karayaithiba paripaktaku amalare punahbiniyoga karayae |  
 ehi parthakya banda kretamana~nka pai.n chintara bishaya hoinapare yeu.nmane kupan deya punahbiniyoga kariba paribartte kharchcha karibaku ichcha karanti, yepariki sampatti/dayit melaka rananiti abhyasa karuthiba kretamana~nka pai.n |

kredit guna 
ehi samasyara gunabatta bandaholdaramane dharyya tarikhare pratishrriti diayaithiba rashi grahana karibara sambhabanaku suchita kare | anya shabdare, kredit gunabatta nibeshakamana~nku kahithae ye rrinagrahita kete sambhabanare diphalta hebaku yauchanti?

bajara mulya 
eka banijyika bandara bajara mulya, anyanya karana madhyare, sudha deyara parimana, mudra ebam samaya ebam pu~nji parishodha, bandara gunabatta ebam anya tulanatmaka bandara upalabdha mukti utpadanadara prabhabita heba yaha banijya hoipariba | bajarare

mulyaku parishkara kimba maila boli kuhayaipare | "maila" samasta bhabishyatara nagada prabahara barttamanara mulya antarbhukta kare, akaunt sudhaku antarbhukta kari, ebam eha prayatah yuropare byabahrrita hue | "parishkara" hisabita sudhaku antarbhukta nahi.n, ebam prayatah yuktarashtrare byabahrrita hue |

isyu mulya yeu.nthire nibeshakamane prathame jari heba samayare banda kinanti taha sadharanatah namamatra parimana sahita praya samana heba | pradanakari grahana karuthiba nit aya heuchi ehipari isyu mulya, kam pradana shulka | bandara bajara mulya ehara jibanare bhinna heba: eha eka primiyamare banijya karipare (samakaksha, sadharanatah karana bajara sudha hara samasya paratharu hrasa paichi), kimba rihatire (samana mulyare, yadi bajara hara brriddhi paichi kimba bandare diphalta hebara adhika sambhabana achi).

User: pushtikara khadyaku prabhabita karuthiba anyanya karyyakramare jatiya madhyahna bhojana yojana, jatiya gramina sasthya mishana ebam jana bitarana byabastha (pds) antarbhukta | ehi programa ebam yojanagudika pai.n ahana heuchi kipari dakshata, prabhaba ebam kabharej brriddhi karayiba |

ehi abhiyana pa~nchati "c" upare adharita:

 communication : acharana paribarttana pai.n yogayoga 
 capacity: kshamata nirmana
 community's access to tangibles and intangibles: drrishya ebam adrrishyaku sampradayara prabesha
 community participation: sampradayara amshagrahana ebam
 collective approach: samuhika abhimukhya
